The world of Steigenberger

   Experience a unique philosophy of hospitality – interpreted
   individually over fifty times.

   Whether it's in a historic building steeped in tradition or a modern
   designer hotel, whether it's in the heart of a fascinating city or
   surrounded by idyllic countryside – you can look forward to a very
   special sense of wellbeing in the establishments of the Steigenberger
   Hotels & Resorts.

